msgctxt "56_Chigusa"
msgid "I have to thank you, Kiryu-san. If I hadn't met you today, I\\r\n"
"might never have come to terms with Yusaku's death."
msgstr "Tengo que darte las gracias, Kiryu. Si hoy no te hubiera\\r\n"
"conocido puede que nuncha hubiera aceptado la muerte\\r\n"
"de Yusaku."

msgctxt "68_Kiryu"
msgid "Hey, you finally called me by the right name."
msgstr "Hey, al fin acertaste mi nombre."

msgctxt "80_Chigusa"
msgid "Yeah... Yeah, I guess I did. I really put you through a lot\\r\n"
"today, huh?"
msgstr "Sí... sí, supongo que sí. Realmente hice que la pasaras\\r\n"
"mal hoy, eh?"

msgctxt "92_Kiryu"
msgid "What, that? It was nothing."
msgstr "¿Qué, eso? No fue nada."

msgctxt "104_Chigusa"
msgid "...Thank you, though. You're an amazing person, Kiryu-san.\\r\n"
"I might even fall for you if I'm not careful."
msgstr "... De todas formas, gracias. Eres una persona increíble,\\r\n"
"Kiryu. Si me descuido podría hasta enamorarme de ti."

msgctxt "116_Chigusa"
msgid "Oh, wait! I still have those engagement rings from earlier.\\r\n"
"Will you marry me, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr "¡Ah, espera! Todavía tengo esos anillos de compromiso.\\r\n"
"¿Te quieres casar conmigo, Kiryu?"

msgctxt "128_Kiryu"
msgid "Uh..."
msgstr "Eh..."

msgctxt "140_Chigusa"
msgid "Haha, just kidding! Another little lie, sorry. You didn't\\r\n"
"believe me, did you?"
msgstr "¡Ja ja, era broma! Otra pequeña mentira, perdón. No\\r\n"
"te lo habrás creído, ¿no?"

msgctxt "164_Kiryu"
msgid "*sigh*"
msgstr "*suspiro*"

msgctxt "176_Chigusa"
msgid "Even so... I want you to have these. I don't need them\\r\n"
"anymore."
msgstr "Aún así... quiero que te quedes esto. Ya no los\\r\n"
"necesito."

msgctxt "212_Kiryu"
msgid "Are you sure?"
msgstr "Tú..."

msgctxt "224_Chigusa"
msgid "Yeah. Yusaku gave me something far more important than\\r\n"
"these rings today."
msgstr "Sí. Yusaku hoy me dio algo mucho más importante que\\r\n"
"estos anillos."

msgctxt "236_Chigusa"
msgid "And it's not just that. If I hang onto them... I don't think\\r\n"
"I'll ever find the strength to move on."
msgstr "Y no solo eso. Si me los quedo... no creo que vuelva\\r\n"
"a encontrar la fuerza para pasar página."

msgctxt "248_Kiryu"
msgid "All right. I'd be honored to take care of them for you."
msgstr "De acuerdo. Será un honor cuidarlos por ti."

msgctxt "260_Chigusa"
msgid "Well, I should be going. Goodbye, Kiryu-san."
msgstr "Bueno, debería irme. Adiós, Kiryu."

msgctxt "284_Kiryu"
msgid "Maybe sometimes lying is the right thing to do..."
msgstr "Puede que a veces mentir sea lo correcto..."

